Find the number of rows and columns in the dataset.
Calculate the mean and median values for each column.
Calculate the standard deviation for each column.
Calculate the minimum and maximum values for each column.
Create a scatter plot of fixed acidity vs. pH.
Create a histogram of alcohol levels.
Identify missing values in the dataset.
Create a boxplot of the quality ratings.
Calculate the correlation between citric acid and pH.
Fit a linear regression model to predict the wine quality based on physicochemical properties.
